OVER HERE TO GIVE TO YOU.

206
00:17:17,875 --> 00:17:20,375
- PLEASE, USE IT
TO RESCUE SAKAI.

207
00:17:20,458 --> 00:17:22,083
- WE'RE BEGGING YOU.

208
