COULD COME UP WITH TO HELP HIM.

210
00:17:28,083 --> 00:17:31,083
- HIRAI, YOU'VE GOTTA
SAVE HIS LIFE, PLEASE!

211
00:17:31,166 --> 00:17:33,375
