YUKARI HIRAI TO SAVE HIM.

213
00:17:36,708 --> 00:17:38,250
- HMM.

214
00:17:38,333 --> 00:17:40,500
- PLEASE HIRAI.
- I BEG YOU.

215
00:17:42,708 --> 00:17:44,291
- Sato: WE'RE GONNA GO
TO THE CRYSTAL ALTAR.

216
00:17:44,375 --> 00:17:45,791
- HUH?

217
00:17:45,875 --> 00:17:47,791
