TO HELP YOU OUT FROM THERE.

218
00:18:03,750 --> 00:18:06,916
- Alastor: ASKING
YUKARI HIRAI...

219
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:09,333
THIS IS THE FIRST TIME
HUMAN BEINGS HAVE EVER

