WANNA SAY IT.

225
00:18:32,291 --> 00:18:36,458
- IF I WAS YOU, YUKARI,
I COULD GO RESCUE HIM.

226
00:18:36,541 --> 00:18:39,291
I CAN'T STAND THIS.
IN A SITUATION LIKE THIS,

227
00:18:39,375 --> 00:18:41,708
YOU AND SAKAI ARE JUST
CLOSER TO EACH OTHER.

228
00:18:41,791 --> 00:18:43,958
- WE'RE CLOSER TO EACH OTHER?

229
00:18:44,041 --> 00:18:45,875
- BUT THAT GIVES ME
FAITH IN YOU.

230
00:18:45,958 --> 00:18:48,041
SO, I BELIEVE IN YOU, YUKARI.

231
00:18:50,833 --> 00:18:54,625
BECAUSE I BELIEVE THE FEELING OF
LOVE IS THE SAME FOR EVERYONE.

232
00:18:54,708 --> 00:18:57,791
I BELIEVE IN YOU, BECAUSE I
THINK YOU REALLY LOVE SAKAI.

233
00:18:59,375 --> 00:19:00,500
- BECAUSE I...

234
00:19:02,875 --> 00:19:04,041
- Wirhelmina: I'VE BEEN
LOOKING FOR YOU.

235
00:19:04,125 --> 00:19:05,291
- HUH?

236
00:19:09,708 --> 00:19:11,083
- IF YOU DON'T GET SOME REST,

237
00:19:11,166 --> 00:19:14,250
THEN YOUR INJURIES WILL INDEED
TAKE LONGER TO HEAL.

238
00:19:14,333 --> 00:19:17,708
DESTROYING THE MYSTES IS A
MATTER OF THE GRAVEST URGENCY.

239
00:19:18,500 --> 00:19:19,666
LET'S BE OFF.

240
00:19:21,458 --> 00:19:24,500
- Yoshida: YUKARI,
I'LL BE WAITING.

241
00:19:24,583 --> 00:19:27,291
COME BACK WITH SAKAI.
I'LL BE WAITING.

242
00:19:32,041 --> 00:19:33,041
- RIGHT.

243
00:19:37,333 --> 00:19:41,833
- OH, PLEASE. I'M SURE YOU'LL DO
IT, BECAUSE I KNOW YOU LOVE HIM.

244
00:19:45,125 --> 00:19:47,041
- YUJI, I CAN FEEL YOU.

245
00:19:49,166 --> 00:19:51,166
- Bel Peol: THIS ENTIRE
CITY WILL BECOME ONE

246
00:19:51,250 --> 00:19:54,083
SOLID MASS OF EXISTENCE.

247
00:19:54,166 --> 00:19:57,833
HAS THERE EVER BEEN ANYONE
WHO HAS GAINED SUCH POWER?

248
00:19:57,916 --> 00:20:02,666
NAY, I, JUDGE OF PARADOXES, WILL
BECOME THE FIRST TO CONTROL IT.

249
00:20:02,750 --> 00:20:03,875
- Sydonay: HECATE.

250
00:20:11,041 --> 00:20:13,416
- WHAT...AM I DOING?

251
00:20:15,291 --> 00:20:17,250
I CAN'T REMEMBER.

252
00:20:17,333 --> 00:20:19,291
I'M SURE I'VE
FORGOTTEN SOMETHING.

253
00:20:22,416 --> 00:20:25,916
- THESE ARE...
THE MEMORIES OF THE MYSTES.

254
00:20:27,125 --> 00:20:30,416
- MY MEMORIES?

255
00:20:30,500 --> 00:20:35,708
- YES, YOUR MEMORIES
ARE FLOWING INTO ME.

256
00:20:35,791 --> 00:20:39,750
- MY, THAT'S RIGHT.
THEY'RE MINE.

257
00:20:41,291 --> 00:20:45,625
- SHANA, DECIDE FOR YOURSELF
WHAT PATH YOU WISH TO TAKE.

258
00:20:46,833 --> 00:20:47,791
- YEAH.

259
00:20:49,833 --> 00:20:51,041
- Yuji: I KNOW HER.

260
00:20:51,833 --> 00:20:52,875
THAT'S...

261
00:20:54,666 --> 00:20:55,958
- YUJI.

262
00:21:02,666 --> 00:21:04,041
- SHANA!

263
00:21:10,083 --> 00:21:11,625
- WELL THEN,
ARE YOU INDEED READY?

264
00:21:11,708 --> 00:21:13,208
- YEAH.

265
00:21:13,291 --> 00:21:16,916
- ONCE WE STORM IN THERE, THERE
WILL INDEED BE NO TURNING BACK.

266
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:18,916
- I KNOW.
- AND OUR OBJECTIVE?

267
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:20,583
- Shana: THE ONLY
THING I'M CERTAIN OF

268
00:21:20,666 --> 00:21:22,583
IS THAT I HAVE TO GO IN THERE.

269
00:21:22,666 --> 00:21:23,916
- I UNDERSTAND.

270
00:21:24,000 --> 00:21:26,541
IF WE GO, I'M SURE THE ANSWER
WILL BECOME CLEAR,

271
00:21:26,625 --> 00:21:29,000
- BECAUSE YOU ARE A FLAME HAZE.
- YEAH.

272
00:21:30,750 --> 00:21:31,708
- Tiamat: ENTER.

273
00:21:38,875 --> 00:21:41,875
- SHANA. SHE PROTECTED ME,

274
00:21:41,958 --> 00:21:43,833
EVEN THOUGH I'M NOTHING
BUT A MYSTES.

275
00:21:46,833 --> 00:21:48,583
WHY?

276
00:21:48,666 --> 00:21:51,375
- ( sighs )
I'M BECOMING FULFILLED...

277
00:21:51,458 --> 00:21:54,833
WITH A MYSTES...
WITH A PERSON.

278
00:21:54,916 --> 00:21:57,250
THOUGHTS DEEP AND STRONG.

279
00:21:57,333 --> 00:22:01,208
I'VE NEVER CONTACTED
SOMETHING LIKE THIS BEFORE.

280
00:22:01,291 --> 00:22:04,458
- SHANA.
- Shana: YUJI, I CAN FEEL YOU.

281
00:22:06,166 --> 00:22:09,541
- THEY'RE COMING.
- OH, YES. I'M READY FOR THEM.

282
00:22:14,666 --> 00:22:17,666
BUT WILL THEY EVEN
MAKE IT THIS FAR?

283
00:22:22,541 --> 00:22:25,000
- SAKAI, YUKARI.

284
00:22:30,041 --> 00:22:32,458
- HIRAI.
- COME ON.

285
00:22:34,958 --> 00:22:37,333
- WHY ARE THERE SO MANY
DENIZENS FROM BALL MASQUE

286
00:22:37,416 --> 00:22:38,916
HANGING AROUND HERE?

287
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:41,708
DO YOU THINK THE PALACE OF STARS
KICKED 'EM OUT?

288
00:22:41,791 --> 00:22:43,750
- Marco: THEY SAY THE RATS ARE
THE FIRST TO FLEE

289
00:22:43,833 --> 00:22:45,125
A SINKING SHIP.

290
00:22:45,208 --> 00:22:47,458
- Margery: HA, THAT THING'S
BASICALLY UNSINKABLE.

291
00:22:47,541 --> 00:22:50,375
ESPECIALLY WITH
THAT HAG, BEL PEOL, IN CHARGE.

292
00:22:50,458 --> 00:22:53,666
BUT, THERE IS SOMETHING
STRANGE GOING ON

293
00:22:53,750 --> 00:22:56,791
- Marco: THESE GUYS MAY BE
ABLE TO ANSWER A FEW QUESTIONS.

294
00:22:56,875 --> 00:23:01,458
- ( chuckles ) THEN LET'S
START ASKING, SHALL WE?

295
00:23:01,541 --> 00:23:05,375
FIRST, I'LL SOFTEN 'EM UP.
THAT'LL HELP 'EM START TALKING.

296
00:23:25,958 --> 00:23:27,375
- ( theme song playing )

297
00:23:27,458 --> 00:23:29,333
- ( singing in Japanese )

298
00:24:57,000 --> 00:25:00,000
- Yuji: SHANA AND WIRHELMINA
ENTER THE PALACE OF STARS

299
00:25:00,083 --> 00:25:02,791
WHERE THEY FALL INTO THE TRAP
BALL MASQUE SET FOR THEM.

300
00:25:02,875 --> 00:25:05,333
THE FINAL BATTLE, FROM WHICH
THERE IS NO TURNING BACK,

301
00:25:05,416 --> 00:25:07,125
IS ABOUT TO BEGIN.

302
00:25:07,208 --> 00:25:10,000
NEXT EPISODE,
"BATTLE AT THE PALACE OF STARS."

